
X-login redirects to original page requested
X-add profile picture upload, username, phone number, middle initial to register
X-fix access log insert issue
X-fix access log table filter issue
X-only allow food banks to shop and reserve food
-add item description page

The web server is hosted on a Debian 9 (Stretch) LXC container running on the type-1 hypervisor Proxmox. 
The web server is configured using the LEMP (Linux, Nginx, MySQL, and PHP) stack.
The MySQL relational database used is MariaDB. 
Domain name is registered using NameCheap.
HTTPS is enabled using an SSL/TLS certificate from certificate authority Let's Encrypt and configured in Nginx using certbot.
Using Postfix 6.4 as an SMTP server